_sText:
Ok, this is my first prefab, and this is intended to be a spawn room, but you can use this as you wish. Program Used.
    VALVe Hammer Editor.
Inspiration.
    I was sitting at my computer and noticed that it would be nice if I could make a Spawn Room. At first I tried to make this as a self taught lesson, and as I progressed I thought it looked pretty nice. I suggest you try this in game because it looks better there.
Guidelines
    You can re-texture this as you wish, also you may add some things to this, but please put my name in the credits. Apart from that you can use this in your map.
